	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			WOW!  Just finished my first venture into Sol A... We were lvl30 Druid, lvl 32 druid, lvl 31 enchanter, and lvl 34 cleric.  What a great dungeon!  Kudos to Veriant.  Had the most fun ever on EQ.  (And thats no lie)  Almost everything you kill has excellent items.  the efreeti, the foreman, Singe...  We will be back, and I look forward to spend the next 4-5 levels of my character there.<BR>
<BR>
Enjoy!<BR>
<BR>
Baldo Leafsway
			</font>
	
